[greta_stonefist]: Ah, greetings there. I do my best with what I've got. What brings you to my forge at such a late hour? Need something sturdy or sharp?
[player]: I can see the quality in every piece you forge. True artistry combined with function.
[greta_stonefist]: Thank you for your kind words. Many seek my skills, but few find what they truly need here. What might I make for you tonight?
