But let me ask you: are you prepared? This isn't just any weapon; it requires a strength and skill that few can match. Can you handle such a burden?
[player]: I promise to wield it with honor and put it to good use defending those who cannot defend themselves.
[greta_stonefist]: Very well, then. Your resolve is clear. Follow me to the forge, and let us see what can be done. The darkness of night will soon give way to the light of your battle against the frost giants.